            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Space Academy, where we inspire the next generation of space explorers! Established in 2020, our academy is dedicated to providing high-quality education and training in the field of space science and exploration.</p>
            <p>Our team of experienced instructors includes former astronauts, scientists, and engineers who are passionate about sharing their knowledge and experience with students. We offer a variety of programs that cover everything from basic astronomy to advanced robotics and spacecraft design.</p>
            <p>At Space Academy, we believe in hands-on learning. Our state-of-the-art facilities and equipment allow students to engage in simulations, workshops, and collaborative projects that prepare them for real-world challenges in space exploration.</p>
            <p>Join us on this exciting journey and unlock your potential in the cosmos!</p>
